In addition to the DT-MRI scan, the sagittal structural volumetric T1-weighted (T1W) images were acquired as follows: TR/TE/TI = 10/4/300 ms, flip angle = 15° and \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
